103
00:06:46,714 --> 00:06:49,635
you can appeal to horse riders and fans of Western films.

104
00:06:49,995 --> 00:06:54,776
A lot of times you can find an audience who don't necessarily play a lot of video games,

105
00:06:54,836 --> 00:06:58,517
but they do have interests that are aligned with the kind of game that you're making.

106
00:07:00,729 --> 00:07:05,534
