00:36:08,302 --> 00:36:12,424
be reaching out to press to and posting everywhere for leading up to your game's launch.

591
00:36:13,104 --> 00:36:15,305
The obvious first one is your game announcement.

592
00:36:15,886 --> 00:36:19,667
If you haven't done this already, make sure when you put up your Steam page and release

