00:37:30,108 --> 00:37:32,608
that's when you want to start reaching out for coverage interest.

612
00:37:33,068 --> 00:37:36,289
You'll want to announce your release date no more than a few months in advance.

613
00:37:36,889 --> 00:37:38,790
If it's too early, people are going to forget about it.

614
00:37:39,390 --> 00:37:42,871
So around the same time that you announce your release date,

615
00:37:43,131 --> 00:37:45,531
or about a month before you actually release your game,

616
00:37:45,931 --> 00:37:48,252
you'll want to start providing review keys to your press

617
00:37:48,312 --> 00:37:49,412
and your content creators.

618
00:37:49,892 --> 00:37:52,113
Make sure you give them plenty of time to review your game.

