00:38:36,010 --> 00:38:37,511
The subject line is something like,

634
00:38:37,932 --> 00:38:40,634
Roguelite Horse FPS Gun Horse releases today!

635
00:38:41,214 --> 00:38:43,997
And in the body of the email include your short description,

636
00:38:44,277 --> 00:38:47,960
your bullet points, a link to the Steam page, a link to your press kit.

637
00:38:48,441 --> 00:38:52,966
Your press release, a nice small-sized GIF or screenshot, and a Steam key.

638
00:38:53,487 --> 00:38:58,453
You don't want to create an extra step by making the press and influencers have to ask you for a key.

