00:39:18,606 --> 00:39:21,810
explain that you'd love to hear their feedback in the form of a Steam review.

645
00:39:22,530 --> 00:39:26,154
And reply to the reviews if you have reviews come in that aren't so positive,

646
00:39:26,334 --> 00:39:28,376
but are calling out specific issues in your game.

