00:39:28,717 --> 00:39:30,699
Like if someone leaves a negative review and says,

648
00:39:30,799 --> 00:39:33,201
there are a lot of bugs and I didn't like it,

649
00:39:33,702 --> 00:39:35,323
you can reply to that review and say,

