00:39:35,404 --> 00:39:36,925
hey, thank you so much for the heads up.

651
00:39:37,145 --> 00:39:40,569
I'm working on these bugs or I've released a patch that addresses these bugs.

652
00:39:40,709 --> 00:39:42,531
I'd love for you to try the game out again.

653
00:39:44,064 --> 00:39:48,106
And then launch with a launch discount. This is standard practice nowadays, so make sure

654
00:39:48,126 --> 00:39:51,967
you've locked, locked in your launch discount at least two weeks before you release your

655
00:39:51,987 --> 00:39:56,549
game on Steam. People are more likely to buy a game when it's on sale, and if it's on sale

656
00:39:56,690 --> 00:39:59,851
when you launch it, they're doubly as likely to buy it.

